# 🧙 Arcane Quest Generator 🐉

> A magical, fantasy-themed quest generator powered by a fine-tuned GPT-2 model. Built with Flask and styled like a medieval scroll, this project brings AI-powered adventures to your browser!

---

## 🌟 Features

- 🔮 Generate fantasy quests based on your input theme or prompt  
- 🧠 Fine-tuned GPT-2 model used for quest generation  
- 📜 Medieval parchment-style UI  
- 🌌 Rotating fantasy background images with smooth fade-in transitions  
- 🧾 Dedicated status page showing model info, uptime, and device  
- 🖋️ Stylized fonts and animations for an immersive fantasy experience  

---

## 🗂️ Folder Structure

fantasy-quest-gen/ │ ├── app.py # Flask backend app ├── requirements.txt # Python dependencies ├── README.md # Project overview (this file) │ ├── model/ # GPT-2 model files (Not pushed to GitHub) │ ├── config.json │ ├── merges.txt │ ├── vocab.json │ ├── tokenizer.json │ └── pytorch_model.bin │ ├── templates/ # HTML templates │ ├── index.html # Main quest generator page │ └── status.html # Arcane Engine status page │ ├── static/ │ ├── style.css # Medieval-themed styles │ └── backgrounds/ # Rotating fantasy background images │ ├── fantasy1.jpg │ ├── fantasy2.webp │ └── fantasy3.jpg

